{"tid":1384350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"體育 【巧固球】港隊殺入世界賽　非港協認可項目零資助　網上眾籌出戰","createTime":"2019-07-30T01:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T01:53:13.000Z","uid":28450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0dac1b44928e21d39764c125cc2af23becb45c25","tid":1384350,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:26:04.000Z","msg":"如果要排先後次序，我都知前線義士緊要啲⋯⋯<br />\n但呢個我都覺得要幫，一百幾十都好<br />\n香港運動需要香港人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年世界巧固球錦標賽將於8月8至11日於馬來西亞舉行。港隊運動員昨自發籌辦集氣大會暨微電影首映，並發起眾籌出戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於巧固球未納入港協暨奧委會認可項目，港隊代表未能在正式的授旗儀式下出戰世界賽。其中男子隊成員李浩璋，更於半年前離職，全力備戰。同時伙拍一眾隊友，進行一連串巧固球推廣，望巧固球及其背後的教育意義能在香港普及。其中的眾籌活動「支援香港巧固球運動員出戰世界賽」及是次集氣大會，皆由他領導和策劃。李浩璋如歡迎辭直言：「巧固球成就了24名球員，我們會以最大的力量和決心成就巧固球發光發熱！」<br />\n<br />\n資源緊絀的情况並未有打擊巧固球港隊出戰的決心，近年自資南征北討出賽，更在全國賽取得佳績，去年在世界賽亞洲區資格賽男女子隊同樣取得16強成績。主禮嘉賓馬逢國議員表示：「運動項目普及化難免受制於場地不足，但巧固球所需的場地空間不大，十分適合在港發展。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20190729/s00006/1564390986668/%e3%80%90%e5%b7%a7%e5%9b%ba%e7%90%83%e3%80%91%e6%b8%af%e9%9a%8a%e6%ae%ba%e5%85%a5%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e8%b3%bd-%e9%9d%9e%e6%b8%af%e5%8d%94%e8%aa%8d%e5%8f%af%e9%a0%85%e7%9b%ae%e9%9b%b6%e8%b3%87%e5%8a%a9-%e7%b6%b2%e4%b8%8a%e7%9c%be%e7%b1%8c%e5%87%ba%e6%88%b0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20190729%2Fs00006%2F1564390986668%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%25b7%25a7%25e5%259b%25ba%25e7%2590%2583%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%259a%258a%25e6%25ae%25ba%25e5%2585%25a5%25e4%25b8%2596%25e7%2595%258c%25e8%25b3%25bd-%25e9%259d%259e%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%258d%2594%25e8%25aa%258d%25e5%258f%25af%25e9%25a0%2585%25e7%259b%25ae%25e9%259b%25b6%25e8%25b3%2587%25e5%258a%25a9-%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e4%25b8%258a%25e7%259c%25be%25e7%25b1%258c%25e5%2587%25ba%25e6%2588%25b0&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=bf5510da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20190729%2Fs00006%2F1564390986668%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%25b7%25a7%25e5%259b%25ba%25e7%2590%2583%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%259a%258a%25e6%25ae%25ba%25e5%2585%25a5%25e4%25b8%2596%25e7%2595%258c%25e8%25b3%25bd-%25e9%259d%259e%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%258d%2594%25e8%25aa%258d%25e5%258f%25af%25e9%25a0%2585%25e7%259b%25ae%25e9%259b%25b6%25e8%25b3%2587%25e5%258a%25a9-%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e4%25b8%258a%25e7%259c%25be%25e7%25b1%258c%25e5%2587%25ba%25e6%2588%25b0&h=eb0ab01d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20190729/s00006/1564390986668/%e3%80%90%e5%b7%a7%e5%9b%ba%e7%90%83%e3%80%91%e6%b8%af%e9%9a%8a%e6%ae%ba%e5%85%a5%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e8%b3%bd-%e9%9d%9e%e6%b8%af%e5%8d%94%e8%aa%8d%e5%8f%af%e9%a0%85%e7%9b%ae%e9%9b%b6%e8%b3%87%e5%8a%a9-%e7%b6%b2%e4%b8%8a%e7%9c%be%e7%b1%8c%e5%87%ba%e6%88%b0</a>"},{"pid":"4adefab7372d06d55ad0e70b2b3126e73a607e73","tid":1384350,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02829fa25cb8d4640f9d6182da0011785bfab2c1","tid":1384350,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"後生既義士就唔洗捐啦<br />\n有能力既大人捐一百幾十都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}